         #       THESE ARE GOOGLE REQUIRED TESTS SO YOU SHOULD NOT DISABLE THEM
         #       IN PRODUCTION RELEASES.
         #       - check_developer_switch: check for developer button switch
         #       - write_protect: enable and check flash ROM write protection
